I was looking for dental clinic when I came across Dental clinic. I visited the clinic for treatment of wisdom teeth. Dr Smita was very helpful. She took a full x-ray and explained all the problems in my teeth. Not only she fixed my current problems, she also fixed a problem I was experiencing from a treatment from some other Doctor. She is very professional and knowledgeable. 
I will recommend it every one as I live in New Zealand and didn’t had such experience there as I got in her clinic. She regularly contacted me after treatment to check on my recovery.

Dr. Smita was friendly and was keen on knowing my problem completely. She explained everything in very simple to understand terms. Her clinic is impeccably clean and all the instruments are very well maintained. I was especially satisfied with how her team took care of hygiene and cleanliness throughout the process. Her team followed up with me even after treatment. I am very happy overall, very satisfied with the doctor and her team and would recommend her to everyone.

The doctor at her clinic explained everything nicely but be amazed by her clinic aura space, talking and highly recommended it. And rest impression remains for after taking treatment. It was my first visit for my two kids there. 👍👌

I was very anxious before the extraction. She was very patient with me and dealt with my anxiety and made me comfortable. I was very relaxed during the procedure and she used the finest of needle for LA and I didn’t feel the pain . Just a slight prick . She understands the need of patient fully . Fully satisfied and would highly recommend .
Lots of luv
